Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:49.04,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:49.04,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让机会溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.29,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.29,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}为什么要剥夺我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.93,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.93,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与感性不同 理性更让我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:59.76,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:59.76,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必须跨越这挫败感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:03.26,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:03.26,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有努力将不会是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.33,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.33,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无尽的欲望 在心中不断反复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.64,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.64,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夹在理想与现实间的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:12.17,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:12.17,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一定有一种可以改变世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.74,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.74,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.04,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.04,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我歌唱得走调又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.12,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.12,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手绘不佳也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:23.88,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:23.88,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我只会为了追寻那唯一的信念而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.53,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.53,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.53,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.53,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:28.87,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“A whole new world god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:28.87,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"一个只有神知道的崭新的世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.77,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.07,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,440)\fs22}I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.77,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我将永远伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.07,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs22}我明白你内心受到的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.97,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.97,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的骑士 做你的明灯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.41,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.41,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我们会无比闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:36.96,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:36.96,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:39.07,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears,everything works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:39.07,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼泪 我们将不再惧怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.60,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.60,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所谓的“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.67,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:46.06,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.67,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:46.06,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这不是现实中的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:48.77,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:48.77,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但我会为你做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:51.89,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:51.89,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不管人生将会发生什么 我都将翻过此页跨上成人的阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.60,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,441)\fs22}Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.60,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,38)\fs22}记住 没人可以批判我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.92,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Every end leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.92,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终结必将迎来新一幕的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.72,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.72,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}度过自己认可的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:00.35,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:02:00.35,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}变的坚强 竭尽所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:04.53,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:04.53,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要回头 继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:07.83,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be yourself…Be happy…It's your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:07.83,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你自己 要开心 因为这是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:09.15,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:09.15,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.24,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Find your love…Find your way…For your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.24,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}为你的人生寻找到爱与归宿
